# Google Cloud Text-to-Speech API key (optional)
# Enables high-quality Norwegian TTS voices (WaveNet/Neural2).
# Without this key, the app falls back to the browser's built-in Web Speech API.
#
# Setup:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Enable the "Cloud Text-to-Speech API"
# 3. Create an API key and restrict it to your domain
# 4. Free tier: 1M chars/month WaveNet, 4M chars/month standard
VITE_GOOGLE_TTS_API_KEY=
